flowRoot.flowPara: USAGE Just insert the SIM card into your phone and you should be good to go! To choose a specific phone number, register an extension on eventphone.de and dial the generated token.

flowPara.flowSpan: This SIM card enables you to access the mobile network provided by the osmocom.org project. Look out for the network 262 (MCC) 42 (MNC).

flowRoot.flowPara: HELP In case of unexpected problems or just out of curiousity, swing by the GSM room, next to the POC.
You can also call DECT subscribers and vice versa.
Dial #100# to see you current extension.
